tand%20interest%20a%20lot%20better%20than%20him%20because%20I've%20had%20to%20really%20use%20interest%20rates.%20We%20should%20have%20interest%20rates%20go%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20nominated%20Powell%20to%20serve%20as%20Fed%20Chair%20in%202017%2C%20during%20his%20first%20term%20as%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20initially%20praised%20Powell%20when%20announcing%20his%20nomination%2C%20saying%20Powell%20would%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bwise%20steward%20of%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20soon%20soured%20on%20his%20choice.%20He%20has%20repeatedly%20called%20for%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EPowell%20to%20lower%20interest%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20April%202019%2C%20Trump%20wrote%20on%20X%2C%20then%20known%20as%20Twitter%2C%20that%20Powell%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-fed-should-cut-interest-rates-2019-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eholding%20back%20the%20US%20stock%20market%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20not%20cutting%20interest%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20recently%2C%20on%20April%2017%2C%20Trump%20wrote%20on%20Truth%20Social%20that%20Powell's%20%26quot%3Btermination%20cannot%20come%20fast%20enough%26quot%3B%20after%20Powell%20said%20Trump's%20sweeping%20tariffs%20on%20the%20world%20could%20result%20in%20higher%20inflation%20and%20weaker%20economic%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20ECB%20is%20expected%20to%20cut%20interest%20rates%20for%20the%207th%20time%2C%20and%20yet%2C%20'Too%20Late'%20Jerome%20Powell%20of%20the%20Fed%2C%20who%20is%20always%20TOO%20LATE%20AND%20WRONG%2C%20yesterday%20issued%20a%20report%20which%20was%20another%2C%20and%20typical%2C%20complete%20'mess!'%26quot%3B%20Trump%20wrote%20in%20his%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20same%20post%2C%20Trump%20said%20Powell's%20%26quot%3Btermination%20cannot%20come%20fast%20enough.%26quot%3B%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EHe%20later%20said%20he%20had%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsid