ts-back-diverse-founders-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESteven%20Bartlett%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20fashion%20designer%20%26quot%3BReal%20Housewives%20of%20New%20York%26quot%3B%20star%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffashion-designer-rebecca-minkoff-shares-her-honest-advice-2019-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERebecca%20Minkoff%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Candace%20Nelson%2C%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcupcake-craze-crumbs-bakery-2011-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efounded%20Sprinkles%20Cupcakes%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20Pizzana%20pizzeria%20chain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELinkedIn's%20new%20video%20push%20comes%20as%20tech%20companies%2C%20from%20Spotify%20to%20YouTube%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finfluencers-are-using-podcasts-to-reinvent-themselves-earn-more-money-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Escramble%20to%20lock%20down%20top%20creator%20talent%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDavang%20Shah%2C%20LinkedIn's%20VP%20of%20marketing%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20effort%20is%20also%20part%20of%20the%20platform's%20increased%20focus%20on%20video.%20Total%20video%20viewership%20is%20up%2036%25%20this%20year%20versus%20last%2C%20and%20video%20creation%20is%20growing%20at%20twice%20the%20rate%20of%20other%20post%20formats%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20LinkedIn%20shows%20will%20focus%20on%20topics%20such%20as%20female%20entrepreneurship%2C%20the%20CEO%20playbook%2C%20and%20artificial%20intelligence.%20The%20other%20creators%20taking%20part%20are%20Shelley%20Zalis%2C%20founder%20of%20The%20Female%20Quotient%3B%20Guy%20Raz%2C%20host%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BHow%20I%20Built%20This%26quot%3B%20podcast%3B%20and%20the%20author%20Bernard%20Marr.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELinkedIn%20said%20more%20shows%20from%20additional%20content%20creators%20are%20in%20the%20works%2C%20though%20the%20company%20plans%20to%20keep%20the%20selection%20highly%20curated%20for%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20shows%20mark%20an%20expansion%20of%20LinkedIn's%20Wire%20Program%2C%20which%20has%20been%20renamed%20BrandLink.%20The%20initial%202023%20to%202024%20launch%20partners%20were%20professional%20news%20publishers%20like%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%2C%20Reuters%2C%20and%20Business%20Insider.%20LinkedIn%20said%20it's%20also%20bringing%20on%20new%20publishers%20this%20year%2C%20including%20The%20Washington%20Post%2C%20Front%20Office%20Sports%2C%20and%20Adweek.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20expansion%20to%20creators%2C%20however%2C%20shows%20how%20influencers%20are%20becoming%20an%20increasingly%20important%20part%20of%20social%20media%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmore-men-news-influencers-on-social-media-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eespecially%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20news%20topics%3C%2Fa%3E.%20While%20LinkedIn%20was%20once%20seen%20as%20a%20largely%20self-promotional%20tool%20for%20job%20seekers%2C%20more%20corners%20of%20the%20business%20community%20%E2%80%94%20from%20venture%20capitalists%2C%20to%20CEOs%2C%20and%20marketers%20%E2%80%94%20are%20regularly%20coming%20to%20the%20platform%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flinkedin-expanding-video-feed-how-creators-grow-audience-tiktok-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eriff%20on%20the%20latest%20news%20and%20other%20trending%20topics%20in%20their%20industries%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20BrandLink%20program%20lets%20the%20publishers%20and%20creators%20monetize%20their%20videos%20through%20pre-roll%20ads%20on%20their%20shows%2C%20which%20appear%20in%20the%20feed%20as%20users%20scroll%20the%20app.%20Like%20YouTube%2C%20users%20can%20skip%20the%20full%20ad%20after%20watching%20for%20a%20few%20seconds.%20Advertisers%20can%20choose%20which%20shows%20they%20want%20to%20appear%20in%20and%20use%20LinkedIn's%20data%20to%20target%20specific%20cohorts%20of%20users%2C%20with%20pricing%20determined%20by%20an%20ad%20auction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELinkedIn%20has%20typically%20kept%20a%2050%25%20cut%20of%20the%20ad%20revenue%20through%20the%20BrandLink%20program%2C%20a%20publisher%20exec%20told%20BI.%20A%20LinkedIn%20spokesperson%20said%20the%20company%20couldn't%20share%20specifics%20about%20the%20revenue%20share%20model.%20Creators%20own%20the%20intellectual%20property%20of%20the%20content%20they%20create%20for%20LinkedIn%2C%20and%20they%20are%20free%20to%20distribute%20the%20content%20on%20other%20platforms%20%E2%80%94%20but%20they%20must%20post%20it%20to%20LinkedIn%20first%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22340d2f43-d5d3-4676-87fe-6d44fb3a1fd0%5C%22%3ELinkedIn's%20professional%2C%20affluent%20audience%20is%20attractive%20to%20advertisers%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELinkedIn%20has%20long%20courted%20creators.%20In%202012%2C%20it%20launched%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fblog%2Fmember%2Farchive%2Fengaging-in-conversations-linkedin-influencer-posts-infographic%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInfluencers%20program%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20encouraging%20famed%20businesspeople%20like%20Bill%20Gates%2C%20Richard%20Branson%2C%20and%20Arianna%20Huffington%20to%20post%20to%20the%20platform.%20But%20its%20efforts%20have%20ramped%20up%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20as%20it's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flinkedin-adds-creator-tools-as-influencer-culture-blends-with-business-2021-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erolled%20out%20tools%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20famous%20and%20everyday%20creators%20alike%2C%20designed%20to%20help%20them%20showcase%20their%20expertise%20and%20boost%20their%20followings.%20Creators%20told%20BI%20last%20year%20that%20they%20had%20seen%20early%20success%20by%20posting%20videos%20to%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flinkedin-expanding-video-feed-how-creators-grow-audience-tiktok-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETikTok-style%20vertical%20video%20feed%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShah%20said%20advertisers%20are%20drawn%20to%20content%20on%20the%20platform%20that%20has%20credibility%20and%20authenticity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20produce%20authentic%20and%20trusted%20content%2C%20it%20leads%20to%20connections%2C%20it%20leads%20to%20conversations%2C%20and%20ultimately%2C%20it%20leads%20to%20closed%20deals%2C%20and%20that's%20what%20marketers%20care%20about%20the%20most%2C%26quot%3B%20Shah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20LinkedIn%2C%20any%20uptick%20in%20user%20numbers%20and%20engagement%20boosts%20its%20advertising%20business.%20Research%20firm%20EMARKETER%2C%20a%20sister%20company%20of%20BI%2C%20forecasts%20that%20LinkedIn%20will%20generate%20%248.06%20billion%20in%20ad%20revenue%20in%202025%2C%20up%2012.4%25%20year-on-year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELinkedIn's%20video%20ambitions%20face%20stiff%20competition%20from%20YouTube%20and%20TikTok%2C%20which%20already%20host%20oodles%20of%20business%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffinance-influencers-share-best-advice-as-tariffs-rock-market-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efinance-focused%20content%3C%2Fa%3E.%20YouTube%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20has%20become%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frise-of-video-podcasts-complications-confusion-advertisers-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etop%20destination%20for%20podcasts%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20the%20aforementioned%20%26quot%3BDiary%20of%20a%20CEO.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrendan%20Gahan%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Creator%20Authority%2C%20an%20influencer%20marketing%20agency%20focused%20on%20LinkedIn%2C%20said%20the%20platform%20has%20its%20advantages%2C%20however.%20It%20ticks%20off%20attributes%20that%20many%20marketers%20want%3A%20A%20large%20audience%20(more%20than%201%20billion%20users%2C%20per%20LinkedIn)%2C%20strong%20ad%20tools%2C%20and%20a%20largely%20brand-safe%20environment.%20Gahan%20said%20what%20sets%20the%20platform%20apart%20is%20its%20professional%2C%20affluent%20niche.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20where%20decision-makers%20and%20executives%20actually%20spend%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Gahan%20said.%20%26quot%3BProbably%20more%20time%20than%20any%20other%20platform.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20LinkedIn%20goes%20all%20in%20on%20video%2C%20Nick%20Cicero%2C%20founder%20of%20Mondo%20Metrics%2C%20an%20analytics%20platform%20and%20data%20consultancy%2C%20said%20the%20platform%20should%20avoid%20chasing%20volume%20over%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLinkedIn%20must%20curate%20high-signal%20content%20that%20matches%20the%20platform's%20professional%20intent%2C%20not%20just%20push%20engagement%20bait%2C%26quot%3B%20Cicero%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20goal%20isn't%20scale%2C%20it's%20signal.%20You%20don't%20need%20a%20million%20views.%20You%20need%20the%20right%2010%20decision-makers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flinkedin-courts-creators-with-new-slate-of-video-shows-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1746072061000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6812423c3fe8d39283647c06%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flinkedin-courts-creators-with-new-slate-of-video-shows-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22LinkedIn%20is%20going%20big%20on%20video%2C%20courting%20creators%20like%20%26quot%3BThe%20Diary%20of%20a%20CEO%26quot%3B%20podcast%20host%20Steven%20Bartlett.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22loreilly%40insider.com%20(Lara%20O'Reilly)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flinkedin-courts-creators-with-new-slate-of-video-shows-2025-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Another%20Simple%20Favor%E2%80%99%20Lands%20on%20Streaming%3A%20Here%E2%80%99s%20How%20to%20Watch%20the%20Sequ