s%20Phos%20The%20Ship%20Hotel%2C%20in%20Bintan%2C%20Indonesia.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20used%20to%20bring%20my%20children%20aboard%20the%20MV%20Doulos%2C%20a%20430-foot-long%20ship%20belonging%20to%20a%20Christian%20missionary%2C%20when%20it%20would%20dock%20on%20Singapore's%20shores.%20It%20had%20spent%2033%20years%20as%20a%20floating%20library%20sailing%20around%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENever%20in%20my%20wildest%20dreams%20did%20I%20ever%20think%20that%20one%20day%20we%20would%20become%20owners%20of%20this%20vessel%2C%20or%20that%20I%20would%20convert%20it%20into%20a%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fbusinessinsider.com%2Fwhat-doulos-phos-like-review-ship-turned-into-beachfront-hotel-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehotel%20on%20the%20shores%20of%20Indonesia%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202010%2C%20I%20bought%20the%20MV%20Doulos%2C%20which%20had%20earned%20the%20Guinness%20World%20Record%20for%20being%20the%20world's%20oldest%20active%20ocean-going%20passenger%20ship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20ship%20has%20won%20accolades%20for%20its%20age%20and%20history%2C%20including%20a%20Guinness%20World%20Record%20for%20being%20the%20oldest%20active%20passenger%20ship.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67b2af666630eb10385ccbe1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20ship%20has%20won%20accolades%20for%20its%20age%20and%20history%2C%20which%20are%20displayed%20in%20its%20lobby.%3Cp%3EAditi%20Bharade%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20built%20in%20Texas%20in%201914%2C%20just%20two%20years%20after%20the%20Titanic%20sank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%201914%20to%201948%2C%20it%20operated%20as%20a%20cargo%20ship%20carrying%20onions.%20I%20often%20joke%20to%20my%20guests%20that%20we%20found%20a%20few%20sacks%20of%20onions%20when%20we%20bought%20the%20ship%20and%20still%20make%20onion%20soup%20from%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20bought%20the%20vessel%2C%20it%20was%2096%20years%20old.%20Here's%20how%20I%20turned%20it%20into%20an%20oceanfront%20hotel%20while%20preserving%20its%20century-old%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c12bda7c-e466-46cc-b3f4-26d443bd89b6%5C%22%3ENot%20my%20first%20rodeo%20with%20ships%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20first%20experience%20with%20ships%20came%20in%202000%20when%20I%20bought%20a%20riverboat%2C%20which%20at%20that%20time%20belonged%20to%20A%26amp%3BW%20Restaurants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20bought%20that%20and%20converted%20it%20into%20a%20floating%20Tex-Mex%20restaurant%20on%20the%20shores%20of%20Sentosa%2C%20an%20island%20off%20Singapore%20known%20for%20its%20luxury%20hotels%2C%20amusement%20parks%2C%20and%20beaches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20heard%20that%20MV%20Doulos%20was%20up%20for%20sale%20in%202010%2C%20I%20saw%20it%20as%20a%20sign%20to%20do%20something%20bigger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20not%20the%20only%20bidder%20for%20the%20ship.%20A%20mix%20of%20private%20companies%2C%20militaries%2C%20and%20scrapyards%20from%20China%2C%20South%20Africa%2C%20South%20Korea%2C%20India%2C%20and%20the%20Philippines%20made%20offers%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20luck%20would%20have%20it%2C%20I%20won%20the%20bid.%20But%20that%20is%20where%20the%20real%20challenges%20started.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20realize%20just%20how%20big%20this%20project%20would%20get.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2259f09d83-209a-4d8f-a92e-4687280feba3%5C%22%3EFinding%20its%20final%20resting%20place%20in%20Bintan%2C%20Indonesia%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20first%20wanted%20to%20dock%20it%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20Singapore.%20I%20placed%20it%20in%20a%20shipyard%2C%20hoping%20that%20within%20three%20months%2C%20I%20would%20get%20approval%20from%20the%20port%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20bargained%20with%20government%20agencies%20for%20permission%20to%20place%20it%20off%20the%20island's%20scenic%20east%20coast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20months%20turned%20into%20three%20and%20a%20half%20years.%20I%20submitted%20six%20to%20seven%20proposals%20to%20various%20authorities%20without%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meantime%2C%20I%20bled%20money%20docking%20and%20maintaining%20the%20ship%20in%20a%20shipyard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20I%20struck%20gold.%20My%20friend%20gave%20me%20the%20number%20of%20Frans%20Gunara%2C%20a%20hotel%20developer%20from%20Bintan%2C%20Indonesia.%20I%20met%20him%20for%20a%20dinner%20presentation%20and%20put%20forth%20my%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20he%20would%20not%20only%20give%20him%20a%20spot%20off%20of%20Bintan%20to%20dock%20the%20ship%20but%20also%20reclaim%20a%20piece%20of%20land%20to%20dry%20berth%20it%2C%20which%20would%20protect%20it%20from%20water%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20decided%20to%20go%20a%20little%20further.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20told%20Frans%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20a%20rectangular%20piece%20of%20land.%20I%20want%20an%20anchor-shaped%20island.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228552d974-339d-4498-8a2e-073a30da749f%5C%22%3ERetrofitting%20the%20ship%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20much%20to%20be%20done%20after%20the%20ship%20had%20been%20placed%20on%20Bintan's%20shores%2C%20on%20its%20anchor-shaped%20piece%20of%20reclaimed%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20innards%20of%20the%20ship%2C%20the%20cabins%2C%20were%20dingy%20and%20small.%20It%20was%20clean%2C%20but%20definitely%20not%20at%20hotel%20standards%20%E2%80%94%20not%20even%20a%20backpackers'%20hotel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20my%20family%20and%20I%20sat%20down%20and%20planned.%20I%20drew%20the%20design%20of%20the%20tables%2C%20the%20interiors%2C%20and%20the%20outdoor%20space.%20I%20drew%20out%20how%20the%20poolside%20would%20look%20and%20where%20you%20would%20go%20down%20to%20do%20the%20mud%20flat%20walk%20at%20low%20tide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20passed%20the%20drawings%20to%20the%20contractors%2C%20and%20they%20started%20constructing.%20Most%20of%20the%20ship%20was%20gutted%20and%20entirely%20retrofitted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20removed%20the%20ship's%20bulkheads%2C%20which%20in%20ocean-going%20ships%20reduce%20damage%20in%20the%20case%20of%20flooding%2C%20we%20had%20to%20reinforce%20the%20structure%20and%20other%20cladding%20to%20protect%20the%20boat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22My%20%26quot%3Bcabin%26quot%3B%20was%20a%20spacious%20executive%20suite.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6736c7d0ede4eeae3927bfdc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20executive%20suite%20in%20the%20ship%20hotel.%3Cp%3EAditi%20Bharade%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cabins%20were%20widened%2C%20and%20we%20added%20larger%20windows%20to%20let%20in%20views%20of%20the%20Bintan%20shores.%20The%20interiors%20were%20designed%20with%20a%20nod%20to%20its%20maritime%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20renovation%2C%20we%20finally%20opened%20our%20doors%20to%20guests%20in%202019.%20Doulos%20Phos%20The%20Ship%20Hotel%20has%20105%20cabins%2C%20an%20infinity%20swimming%20pool%20overlooking%20the%20sea%2C%20a%20gym%2C%20a%20spa%20center%2C%20and%20several%20eateries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20nearly%2010%20years%20to%20restore%20MV%20Doulos%20and%20get%20it%20into%20operation%2C%20but%20I%20saw%20the%20project%20as%20a%20higher%20calling%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20was%20entirely%20worth%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeet-singaporean-who-converted-century-old-ship-into-beachfront-hotel-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1746058681000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67209a7401ea6d83dee4a5e6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeet-singapor