ally%20appreciate%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Huang%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWithout%20energy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe%20can't%20possibly%20have%20new%20growth%20industries.%20And%20we%20now%20have%20the%20backing%20of%20the%20administration%2C%20the%20backing%20of%20President%20Trump%2C%20to%20support%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20whole%20new%20industry.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjensen-huang-says-us-china-very-close-ai-chip-race-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1746051266000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68127444c6ad288d147f9d95%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjensen-huang-says-us-china-very-close-ai-chip-race-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jensen%20Huang%20highlighted%20the%20US-China%20competition%20in%20AI%20chips%2C%20urging%20Trump%20to%20consider%20policies%20that%20open%20up%20US%20chip%20sales%20to%20other%20countries.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ggoodwin%40businessinsider.com%20(Grace%20Eliza%20Goodwin%2CLloyd%20Lee)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A130%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjensen-huang-says-us-china-very-close-ai-chip-race-2025-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kit%20Harington%20Recalls%20the%20%E2%80%98Humiliating%E2%80%99%20Experience%20of%20Bella%20Ramsey%20Telling%20Him%20His%20Lines%20on%20%E2%80%98Game%20of%20Thrones%E2%80%99%3A%20%E2%80%98That%20Child%20Actor%20Is%20Wiping%20Me%20Off%20the%20Screen%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1746049987000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fkit-bella-split.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236383116%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Before%20they%20led%20their%20own%20HBO%20a