king%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d6349187-496b-455c-bc4b-f8eefb761b09%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Picture%20performance%5C%22%3EThe%20QM6K%20delivers%20good%20entry-level%20HDR%20performance%2C%20but%20it's%20dimmer%20than%20pricier%20TVs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222299%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20TCL%20QM6K%20TV%20displaying%20an%20image%20of%20a%20cityscape%20during%20the%20day.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681274883fe8d39283648942%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221724%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20TV's%20Mini%20LED%20backlight%20enables%20solid%20contrast%20for%20a%20display%20in%20this%20class.%3Cp%3ESteven%20Cohen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20QM6K%20is%20positioned%20as%20the%20entry-level%20model%20in%20TCL's%20premier%20lineup%20of%20QLED%20TVs.%20And%20within%20that%20context%2C%20its%20picture%20quality%20is%20impressive.%20Brightness%20and%20contrast%20can't%20match%20that%20of%20the%20brand's%20step-up%20QM7%20or%20QM8%20series%2C%20but%20for%20this%20tier%2C%20the%20QM6K%20is%20a%20great%20performer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20evaluated%20the%20QM6K's%20image%20performance%20using%20a%20mix%20of%20test%20patterns%20and%20real-world%20content%20from%204K%20Blu-ray%20discs%20and%20streaming%20services%2C%20all%20curated%20to%20highlight%20features%20like%20contrast%2C%20local%20dimming%2C%20black%20levels%2C%20color%2C%20and%20upscaling.%20I%20also%20used%20a%20colorimeter%20to%20measure%20the%20display's%20peak%20brightness%2C%20an%20essential%20component%20of%20a%20TV's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-hdr-tv%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigh-dynamic-range%3C%2Fa%3E%20(HDR)%20capabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20TV%20set%20in%20Filmmaker%20Mode%2C%20I%20recorded%20a%20peak%20of%20557%20nits%20on%20a%2010%25%20HDR%20test%20pattern%20(a%20white%20box%20that%20takes%20up%2010%25%20of%20the%20screen).%20The%20brightest%20the%20TV%20got%20was%20with%20a%20larger%2050%25%20test%20pattern%2C%20which%20put%20out%20about%20736%20nits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20are%20both%20decent%20numbers%20for%20an%20entry-level%20HDR%20TV%20like%20this%2C%20and%20they're%20a%20nice%20step%20up%20from%20last%20year's%20Q65%2C%20which%20could%20only%20hit%20about%20400%20nits.%20However%2C%20the%20QM6K's%20brightness%20is%20still%20notably%20lower%20than%20that%20of%20midrange%20TVs%2C%20which%20are%20capable%20of%20about%201%2C000%20to%201%2C500%20nits%2C%20and%20high-end%20sets%20that%20can%20offer%202%2C000%20to%204%2C000%20nits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222177%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20TCL%20QM6K%20TV%20displaying%20a%20collage%20of%20red%20roses.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68127bcb3fe8d39283648b17%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221633%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20QM6K%20can%20produce%20rich%20colors%2C%20but%20its%20brightness%20is%20limited%20compared%20to%20higher-end%20models.%3Cp%3ESteven%20Cohen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20practice%2C%20the%20QM6K's%20brightness%20leads%20to%20good%20but%20not%20great%20HDR%20image%20quality.%20Vivid%20movies%20like%20%26quot%3BAquaman%26quot%3B%20appear%20relatively%20vibrant%20with%20rich%20colors%2C%20but%20highlights%20like%20explosions%2C%20shimmering%20armor%2C%20and%20sunsets%20lack%20some%20of%20the%20boldness%20and%20overall%20pop%20they%20offer%20on%20higher-end%20TVs%20with%20more%20intense%20brightness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMad%20Max%3A%20Fury%20Road%26quot%3B%20reveals%20similar%20limitations.%20Lightning%20bolts%20and%20rippling%20flames%20look%20duller%20than%20on%20step-up%20TV%20models%2C%20lacking%20the%20extreme%20impact%20that%20the%20movie's%20exaggerated%20style%20demands.%20Don't%20get%20me%20wrong%2C%20the%20QM6K%20still%20offers%20a%20solid%20HDR%20picture%2C%20especially%20for%20this%20tier%2C%20but%20the%20set's%20dimmer%20image%20is%20noticeable%20when%20watching%20high-contrast%20HDR%20movies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20QM6K%20uses%20a%20Mini%20LED%20backlight%20with%20local%20dimming%20to%20control%20its%20light%20output.%20This%20enables%20the%20TV%20to%20brighten%20and%20darken%20specific%20areas%20of%20its%20screen%20across%20multiple%20zones.%20Last%20year's%20Q65%20didn't%20have%20local%20dimming%20at%20all%2C%20so%20the%20QM6K%20offers%20a%20huge%20jump%20in%20contrast%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20QM6K%20doesn't%20have%20as%20many%20zones%20to%20work%20with%20as%20pricier%20models%2C%20but%20TCL's%20dimming%20algorithm%20works%20well%20to%20produce%20solid%20black%20levels%20and%20very%20minimal%20blooming%20(halos%20around%20bright%20objects).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20TV's%20dimming%20behavior%20favors%20slightly%20raising%20black%20levels%20to%20preserve%20shadow%20detail%20and%20avoid%20halos.%20Though%20this%20often%20prevents%20the%20QM6K%20from%20producing%20black%20levels%20that%20completely%20disappear%20into%20a%20dark%20room%2C%20it%20does%20help%20to%20create%20a%20more%20even%20image%20that's%20free%20from%20the%20patchy%20brightness%20that%20sometimes%20plagues%20dark%20scenes%20on%20TVs%20with%20more%20aggressive%20dimming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20burning%20church%20scene%20in%20the%20film%20%26quot%3B1917%26quot%3B%20is%20a%20great%20example.%20Though%20I've%20seen%20deeper%20black%20levels%20and%20brighter%20highlights%20on%20other%20Mini%20LED%20TVs%2C%20those%20displays%20tend%20to%20create%20a%20vignetting%20effect%20around%20light%20sources.%20The%20QM6K%20has%20lighter%20black%20levels%20and%20dimmer%20highlights%20overall%2C%20but%20it%20presents%20more%20seamless%20transitions%20between%20this%20sequence's%20dark%20and%20light%20portions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20QM6K%20isn't%20completely%20free%20from%20blooming%2C%20as%20I%20did%20notice%20some%20faint%20halos%20around%20lights%20during%20panning%20shots%20in%20%26quot%3BThe%20Matrix%26quot%3B%20and%20an%20episode%20of%20%26quot%3BChilling%20Adventures%20of%20Sabrina.%26quot%3B%20But%20these%20instances%20are%20subtle%2C%20and%20the%20QM6K%20actually%20handles%20blooming%20a%20bit%20better%20than%20brighter%20Mini%20LED%20TVs%20I've%20tested%2C%20like%20last%20year's%20mid-tier%20QM7%20and%20Hisense's%20premium%20U9N.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222283%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20angled%20image%20of%20a%20TCL%20QM6K%20TV%20displaying%20the%20%26quot%3BSpider-Man%26quot%3B%20PS5%20video%20game.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6812735cc6ad288d147f9d66%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221713%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20QM6K%20supports%20a%204K%2F120Hz%20signal%20with%20gaming%20consoles%20like%20a%20PS5.%3Cp%3ESteven%20Cohen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20color%20smoothness%20and%20stability%20are%20also%20great.%20I%20didn't%20encounter%20any%20egregious%20signs%20of%20banding%20or%20false%20contouring%20(blocky%20and%20pixelated%20colors)%20when%20watching%20various%20sources.%20I%20ran%20into%20this%20problem%20when%20testing%20last%20year's%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15109175648c1-20%26h%3D570bffb6a7e5981ee20026a583abe0f32050f4bc1507a06e76bfefd50f1e4e81%26postID%3D681265f13d37c2e3ad59e4c9%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Ftcl-qm6k-qled-4k-tv-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FHisense-55-Inch-Mini-LED-Google-55U6N%252Fdp%252FB0CY4NKVXF%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHisense%20U6N%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20offers%20similar%20specs%2C%20so%20it's%20nice%20to%20see%20a%20TV%20in%20this%20class%20avoid%20this%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20QM6K%20slightly%20improves%20upon%20another%20area%20where%20many%20QLED%20TVs%20falter%3A%20viewing%20angles.%20The%20TV's%20colors%20and%20contrast%20still%20noticeably%20fade%20and%20distort%20when%20you%20sit%20off-center%20from%20the%20screen%2C%20but%20this%20effect%20is%20less%20severe%20than%20I've%20seen%20on%20some%20other%20entry-level%20sets.%20However%2C%20OLED%20TVs%20and%20pricier%20Samsung%20QLEDs%20still%20have%20a%20big%20edge%20with%20viewing%20angles%2C%20so%20this%20remains%20a%20factor%20to%20remember%20when%20deciding%20between%20a%20budget-friendly%20TV%20and%20a%20more%20expensive%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20plus%20side%2C%20the%20QM6K's%20gaming%20capabilities%20are%20a%20nice%20upgrade%20from%20previous-generation%20models%20in%20this%20class.%20Sets%20in%20this%20tier%20used%20to%20max%20out%20at%2060Hz%2C%20but%20the%20QM6K%20supports%20up%20to%20144Hz%20with%20variable%20refresh%20rate%20(VRR)%20and%20auto%20low%20latency%20mode%20(ALLM).%20This%20means%20the%20TV%20can%20receive%204K%2F120Hz%20signals%20from%20a%20PS5%20or%20Xbox%20Series%20X%2C%20enabling%20you%20to%20enjoy%20the%20smoothest%20gameplay%20possible%20on%20those%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221d553085-5204-4cc9-967b-c31424ee776b%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Smart%20TV%20features%5C%22%3EThe%20TV's%20interface%20works%20well%2C%20with%20fewer%20glitches%20than%20previous%20TCL%20models%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222291%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20angled%20view%20of%20the%20Google%20TV%20homescreen%20recommending%20%26quot%3BWicked%26quot%3B%20on%20a%20TCL%20QM6K%20TV.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68127b473fe8d39283648af7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221718%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGoogle%20TV%20does%20a%20good%20job%20of%20recommending%20content%20that%20suits%20your%20viewing%20habits.%20%3Cp%3ESteven%20Cohen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20QM6K%20uses%20the%20Google%20TV%20operating%20system%2C%20and%20this%20interface%20has%20become%20one%20of%20my%20favorites.%20It%20does%20a%20nice%20job%20of%20highlighting%20your%20downloaded%20apps%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20homepage%20while%20still%20offering%20useful%20rows%20of%20content%20recommendations%20below.%20Unlike%20some%20other%20platforms%20(like%20Fire%20TV)%2C%20which%20put%20too%20much%20emphasis%20on%20sponsored%20content%2C%20Google%20TV%20does%20a%20solid%20job%20of%20curating%20picks%20you%20might%20actually%20want%20to%20watch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20Google%20TV%20tends%20to%20be%20a%20bit%20sluggish%20on%20entry-level%20displays%2C%20that's%20not%20the%20case%20here.%20The%20QM6K%20offers%20smoother%20navigation%20and%20snappier%20app%20selection%20than%20competing%20Hisense%20Google%20TVs%20that%20I've%20tested%20in%20this%20class.%20I%20also%20ran%20into%20fewer%20glitches%20than%20I%20have%20on%20other%20TCL%20and%20Hisense%20sets.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20I've%20run%20into%20odd%20quirks%20like%20incorrect%20picture%20modes%20activating%20and%20certain%20settings%20applying%20incorrectly%20on%20some%20TCL%20TVs.%20But%20on%20the%20QM6K%2C%20none%20of%20those%20issues%20popped%20up.%20This%20is%20a%20promising%20sign%20that%20TCL%20may%20have%20finally%20solved%20some%20of%20its%20most%20prevalent%20software%20bugs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20not%20to%20say%20the%20system%20is%20completely%20without%20hiccups.%20I%20encountered%20lag%20when%20playing%204K%20HDR%20videos%20on%20YouTube%20(a%20common%20issue%20on%20many%20entry-%20and%20mid-tier%20smart%20TVs)%2C%20and%20moving%20through%20various%20services%20and%20menu%20screens%20isn't%20quite%20as%20seamless%20as%20it%20is%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-streaming-devices%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20streaming%20devices%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20in%20general%2C%20most%20people%20should%20be%20more%20than%20satisfied%20with%20the%20built-in%20interface.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20included%20back-lit%20remote%20supports%20Google%20Assis