tion%2C%20water%20scarcity%2C%20and%20pollution.%20Organisations%20like%20Development%20Alternatives%20(DA)%20work%20alongside%20vulnerable%20communities%2C%20empowering%20women%20through%20skill%20development%20and%20economic%20opportunities%2C%20which%20ripple%20out%20to%20improve%20education%2C%20healthcare%2C%20and%20household%20well-being.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmpowering%20women%20not%20only%20uplifts%20individuals%20but%20also%20benefits%20entire%20communities%2C%20breaking%20cycles%20of%20intergenerational%20poverty%20and%20creating%20lasting%2C%20positive%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EKey%20partnerships%20and%20collaborative%20efforts%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDevelopment%20Alternatives%E2%80%99%20green%20entrepreneurial%20ecosystems%20provide%20underserved%20groups%20with%20the%20resources%2C%20opportunities%2C%20and%20market%20linkages%20they%20need%20to%20succeed.%20Their%20approach%20to%20social%20innovation%20focuses%20on%20identifying%20systemic%20challenges%2C%20designing%20solutions%20tailored%20to%20local%20contexts%2C%20and%20enabling%20collaboration%20among%20stakeholders.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20community-based%20model%20centres%20on%20collective%20action%2C%20knowledge%20empowerment%2C%20and%20building%20leadership%20skills%20to%20create%20sustainable%2C%20inclusive%2C%20and%20green%20enterprises.%20By%20leveraging%20partnerships%20and%20facilitating%20co-creation%2C%20they%20ensure%20scalable%20and%20sustainable%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Khushi%20Arora%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1745846244000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FTBI-featured-image-8_11zon-1745845087.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D423566%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20article%20is%20sponsored%20by%20Development%20Alternatives.%20Meenu%20Devi%2C%20a%2036-year-old%20entrepreneur%20from%20Sikhar%2C%20Mi